## Cache headers para evitar stale code
/*.js  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
/*.css  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate
/index.html  Cache-Control: public, max-age=0, must-revalidate

## Session storage - nunca cachear
/auth  Cache-Control: private, no-cache, no-store
/home  Cache-Control: private, no-cache, no-store
/business/*  Cache-Control: private, no-cache, no-store
/cards/*  Cache-Control: private, no-cache, no-store
/profile  Cache-Control: private, no-cache, no-store
